description: Try our easy to follow Speedy Honey & Soy Chicken Stir-Fry recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Stir-fry,Seafood free,Egg free,Spring,Low sugar,Sesame free,Quick & easy dinner,High protein,High fibre,Chicken,Dinner Made Easy,Dairy free
name: Speedy Honey & Soy Chicken StirFry Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 0.33 cup dry roasted cashews, roughly chopped

recipeInstructions.text: Place noodles in a large heatproof bowl and cover with boiling water. Stand for 3 minutes or until tender. Drain.

Meanwhile, using a fork, remove chicken from skewers. Heat a wok over mediumhigh heat. Add 1 tbs vegetable oil, swirling to coat. Stir-fry chicken for 5 minutes or until just cooked through. Transfer to a bowl and cover to keep warm.
Add 2 tsp vegetable oil to wok. Stirfry vegetables for 4 minutes or until just tender. Add noodles, tossing to combine.
Divide stirfry among bowls, scatter over cashews and serve.
